**"From a Solo Project to a Core Business Model"**

CameraFi Studio is a web platform that allows users to overlay scoreboards, subtitles, and graphics onto sports matches or broadcast feeds.
I **architected the frontend from scratch as a solo developer** during the initial planning phase, and successfully grew it into the company's second main revenue stream.

To support a global user base, I implemented **i18n** and a **unified payment system (Paddle)**, and optimized web application performance through **custom Webpack tuning**.

