1. **Tree Shaking:** Removed unused modules from heavy libraries like `lodash`.
2. **Dynamic Import:** Asynchronously loaded non-critical components (charts, heavy modals) to reduce the initial payload.

Through these measures, I **reduced the main bundle size by approx. 15% (47KB)**, significantly improving Time to Interactive (TTI).

