### 2. Enhanced Unified Authentication System

Instead of relying solely on libraries, I designed a secure login process combining **Firebase Custom Tokens** and **Cookies**.
By synchronizing authentication state between client and server via cookies, I enhanced security and built a **unified login interface**, laying the foundation for Single Sign-On (SSO) across multiple services.

### 3. Global Service Architecture

Implemented an **i18n** system from day one to cater to a global audience.
Additionally, I established a **Custom Global Theme** by combining **MUI** and **Styled-components**, creating a flexible UI structure capable of adapting to branding changes and Dark Mode requirements.

### 4. Self-Implemented Compliance (Cookie Consent)

To comply with global web standards like GDPR, I **developed the Cookie Consent banner and control logic internally** without relying on third-party tools. This minimized external script dependencies and prevented page load degradation.

